<lb n="2" break="no"/>mutupaṭikku Ivarkaḷ nammaivantu veṇṭikkoṇṭamaiyil nāḷ Oṉṟukku Amutupaṭi Arici patiṉaṟu nāḻiyāka muttavāṭ kutiraic cevakattile <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>koṇṭu celuttivi<unclear>ṭu</unclear>vārkaḷāka nammolai kuṭuttom I<unclear>p</unclear>paṭikku cempiluñ cilaiyilum veṭṭikkoḷka yāṇṭu Irupattoṉṟāvatu nāḷ Eṇpattiraṇṭu
<lb n="4"/>Itu ca<hi rend="grantha">ntrādi</hi>ttavaṟcelvatāka Itu paṉ<hi rend="grantha">maheśvararakṣai <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi>
